title: 820-2936 green light, no battery charge
message:
Hello I have an 820-2936 that can turn on from the battery but is not taking a charge (shows charging in right top corner but not in hardware overview). Measured following:

PPBUS_G3H   =   12.6
PP3V42_G3H   =   3.47
PP5V_S5   =   Switching on/off when on AC Charger

U7000:
ACIN Pin 3 =  3.98
BCAcok = 3.32
DCIN Pin 2 = 16.04 (when fan turns on goes to 16.27
R7010 & 11 are OK
R7021 & 22 are OK

How do these values look?

title: 820-2936 green light, no battery charge
message: I found R7052 is not 0 but flashing around will try to replace
